data.description: Prepare to be delighted when you walk through the door of this Mt.Shasta charmer! This home is sure to please everyone with it's beautiful finishes.  The kitchen is large and inviting with custom counter tops & cabinets & eating bar that is open to the large living room. Beautiful dark laminate flooring throughout, built ins for storage,  pocket doors, and HUGE view of Majestic Mt.Shasta from the front porch, front room & bedroom, and from the private and large back yard! The front yard is full of beautiful rose bushes with custom natural rock walking path, all surrounded by a wrought iron fence. The back yard is a template that dreams are made of, room for a garden, possible ADU, and home to grapes, cherries, apricots, pears, apples, peaches, plums, and beautiful & tall lilacs...and you won't believe the view of Mt.Shasta! Very large and bright basement ready for your home office, hobbies, she cave, you name it, heated with a monitor heater and abundant shelving for storage. Detached single car garage with wood storage and chicken coup...and RV parking alongside. And the cherry on top- with an acceptable offer furniture is included!!!! You need to come and take a look!
